NAME
    WordList::ZH::Simplified::BIP39 - Chinese word list for BIP 39
    (simplified)

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.001 of WordList::ZH::Simplified::BIP39
    (from Perl distribution WordList-ZH-Simplified-BIP39), released on
    2017-12-24.

SYNOPSIS
     use WordList::ZH::Simplified::BIP39;

     my $wl = WordList::ZH::Simplified::BIP39->new;

     # Pick a (or several) random word(s) from the list
     my $word = $wl->pick;
     my @words = $wl->pick(3);

     # Check if a word exists in the list
     if ($wl->word_exists('foo')) { ... }

     # Call a callback for each word
     $wl->each_word(sub { my $word = shift; ... });

     # Get all the words
     my @all_words = $wl->all_words;

STATISTICS
     +----------------------------------+-------+
     | key                              | value |
     +----------------------------------+-------+
     | avg_word_len                     | 1     |
     | longest_word_len                 | 1     |
     | num_words                        | 2048  |
     | num_words_contains_nonword_chars | 0     |
     | num_words_contains_unicode       | 2048  |
     | num_words_contains_whitespace    | 0     |
     | shortest_word_len                | 1     |
     +----------------------------------+-------+

    The statistics is available in the %STATS package variable.

